Version 0.1 (Jun 21, 2011):

* First public release.

Version 0.2 (Jun 24, 2011):

* Minor bug fixes
* Added support to detect deleted files in one pass
* Added the ability to diff more than two directory trees

Version 0.3 (Jun 27, 2011):

* Added support for more difference tests and a quick (-q) mode

Version 0.4 (July 11, 2011):

* Added md5 support

Version 0.5 (July 17, 2011):

* Minor bug fixes and porting
* Fixed several memory leaks in the hash code
* Added ability to save directory metadata
* Added ability to load previous saves

Version 0.5.2 (October 21, 2011):

* Minor bug fixes

Version 0.5.6 (September 5, 2015):

* Minor bug fixes
* Added some edge-case argument handling
* Added SHA256 hashing

Version 0.5.8 (December 29, 2015):

* Minor bug fixes
* Added atime change detection
* Added atime preservation option

Version 0.5.9 (March 26, 2016):

* Minor bug fixes

Version 0.6.0 (December 29, 2017):

* Minor bug fixes

Version 0.6.1 (June 5, 2018):

* Minor bug fixes

Version 0.6.3 (March 1, 2022):

* Updated hash and parser code and minor bug fixes

Version 1.0.0 (March 4, 2022):

* Improved exclude functionality
* Minor memory leak fixed
* Addressed nftw() uninitilized stat struct

Version 1.0.1 (March 11, 2022):

* Minor cleanups of documentation

Version 1.0.2 (March 14, 2022):

* Minor porting for openBSD 64bit

Version 1.0.3 (October 2, 2024):

* Added support for Tom Liston PINEAPPLE mode

Version 1.0.5 (August 9, 2025):

* Fixed all compiler warnings for clean compilation
* Fixed debug build errors when using --enable-debug
* Improved code quality by addressing unused variables and functions
* Enhanced conditional compilation for DEBUG-specific code
* Improved maintainability and reduced technical debt
